Coding Question: Merge Overlapping Time Intervals

You are given a list of meeting time intervals.

Each interval is represented as:

[start_time, end_time]

Your task is to merge all overlapping intervals and return the merged list.

Example
Input:
[[1,3], [2,6], [8,10], [15,18]]

Output:
[[1,6], [8,10], [15,18]]
